            "title": "【異動板塊】美國對華關稅再加 出口手機股遭拋售",
            "description": "<p>美國白宮對華關稅周三將升到至少104%，出口及手機股遭拋售。</p>\n<p>創科(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/00669' >00669</a>)急跌6.3%；申洲(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/02313' >02313</a>)瀉5.7%；聯想(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/00992' >00992</a>)急跌11.2%；泉峰(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/00285' >00285</a>)大跌9.1%；裕元(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/00551' >00551</a>)瀉6%；晶苑(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/02232' >02232</a>)挫5.1%；德昌(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/00179' >00179</a>)挫6.5%。</p>\n<p>手機股高偉電子(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/01415' >01415</a>)急跌9.9%；瑞聲(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/02018' >02018</a>)急跌8.2%；舜宇(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/02382' >02382</a>)急跌9.4%；比亞迪電子(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/00285' >00285</a>)急跌6.8%；鴻騰(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/06088' >06088</a>)急跌7.6%。</p>\n<p>據美國有線新聞網絡(CNN)周二引述白宮新聞秘書萊維特(Karoline Leavitt)宣布，總統特朗普將於周三對所有中國進口商品徵收額外84%的關稅，這意味着中國所有商品都將被徵收至少104%的關稅。</p>\n<p>立即試用<a href=\"https://www.ejfq.com/home.htm?source=sapo9\" target=\"_blank\">EJFQ「信號」全方位股票分析系統</a>，運用100+選股條件篩選值博股！</p>   </div>\n        ",
